nodes.Entity
id	label	inferred	assumption
BirdObservation	BirdObservation	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
Species	Species	false	Natural key: normalized_scientific_name (lowercase/trim/strip trailing parenthetical authorship). eBird wins descriptive conflicts; GBIF fills taxon identifiers/gaps; Xeno-canto supplies media context. Union coverage across all sources.
BirdHotspot	BirdHotspot	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
RegionDailyStats	RegionDailyStats	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
WeatherObservation	WeatherObservation	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
WeatherStation	WeatherStation	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
StreamflowObservation	StreamflowObservation	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
StreamgageSite	StreamgageSite	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
EarthquakeEvent	EarthquakeEvent	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.

BirdOccurrence	BirdOccurrence	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required.
BirdSoundRecording	BirdSoundRecording	false	No cross-source natural key/stitching strategy required. Audio remains an external linked artifact; CDM stores metadata and URLs only.

